Name: Do Something
About the game: You buy a game that you can pass to the end. Future updates are free of charge. The game is an exploratory zombie shooter with puzzles. After a few hours of epidemic, you go straight to the center to find a secret descent to the laboratory and destroy the virus... You play as Alice, a former operative, who comes to the center of one place, where according to information there should be a secret path to the laboratory where they created the 'D' virus. - Navigate through dangerous terrain, planning your route as you go. - Make it easy on yourself. Look for different keys and tools that will open up workarounds for you. - Realistic graphics and complete adaptation of the interface for 4K. - Full Xbox/DualShock/DualSense gamepad support. - AMD FSR support. Boost your frame rate with FidelityFX Super Resolution smart upscaling.
